title: On a multiplier operator induced by the Schwarzian derivative of a univalent function. (arXiv:2211.01742v1 [math.CV])
description: In this paper we study a multiplier operator which is induced by the Schwarzian derivative of a univalent function with a qc extension to the extended complex plane. We obtain a norm estimate for this operator. As an application, we prove that the Brennan's conjecture is true for a large class of quasi-disks. We also present a new characterization of the asymptotically conformal curves and the WP curves in terms of the multiplier operator.
